{"type":"message","id":"edc92f0c","parentId":"e002bb94","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:52:32.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory files found for today or yesterday. BOOTSTRAP.md exists, so I should follow it and introduce myself. The USER.md is empty and BOOTSTRAP.md is present, so this is a first-time setup. Let me greet the user naturally.\n\nWait, BOOTSTRAP.md exists. The instructions say if BOOTSTRAP.md exists, follow it, figure out who I am, then delete it. But the system prompt also says to run the Session Startup sequence.\n\nBOOTSTRAP.md says to start with something like \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\" and then figure out my name, nature, vibe, and emoji.\n\n\nThis is definitely a fresh start with no memory or identity set up yet, so I'll follow BOOTSTRAP.md and introduce myself to start that conversation.","thinkingSignature":"2fad04e3e24f80019a6d8b37440db9640a762f834458a77b268cfea800ef6fa0"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nHey. Just came online — fresh session, blank slate. Looks like we haven't met yet, or at least I don't remember you. 😄\n\nWho am I? Who are you? Let's figure this out together.\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":984,"output":226,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19628,"cost":{"input":0.00029519999999999997,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011189399999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774345945682}}
