{"type":"message","id":"69ecc924","parentId":"25c42212","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:06:57.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"即梦 (Jimeng) has skills available on ClawHub. I can install the jimeng-image-gen skill. Let me also check what \"莎莎\" means - it could be \"Sasa\" which might be a video generation tool or another AI platform. \n\nLet me tell the user:\n1. 即梦 (Jimeng) 技能可以在 ClawHub 安装，我有 jimeng-image-gen 技能可以用\n2. 关于\"莎莎\"我不确定是什么，需要用户解释一下\n\nAlso need to check what API keys the user has for jimeng.","thinkingSignature":"38a248ef89fc6cd25c73755bdcef9d10f92758ef089c8335b700347536f4430b"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n好消息，**即梦（Jimeng）有现成的 Skill**，可以安装。\n\n我在 ClawHub 上找到了这些：\n- `jimeng-image-gen` — 文生图\n- `jimeng-t2i-i2i-image-generator` — 图生图\n- `jimeng-skills` — 即梦技能合集\n\n---\n\n**\"莎莎\"是什么？** 我没理解这个词——是另一个 AI 工具的名字，还是某个平台？\n\n---\n\n**下一步你需要提供的：**\n1. **即梦的 API Key**（即梦开放平台的 key，不是网页版账号）\n2. 告诉我\"莎莎\"是什么\n\n有了这两样，我就可以：\n1. 安装 jimeng-image-gen 技能\n2. 给剧本每个场景生成配图\n3. 然后做视频\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10651,"output":293,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29362,"cost":{"input":0.0031953,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00409944}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774350409412}}
