{"type":"message","id":"f57ee344","parentId":"51775734","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:08:17.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what other APIs they need to provide besides Jimeng. Let me think about what we need for the full video pipeline:\n\n1. **Jimeng (即梦)** - for image generation (文生图) - already identified\n2. **TTS (Text-to-Speech)** - for voiceover narration - need to check what's available\n3. **Video generation (图生视频)** - to animate the static images\n\nFor a complete pipeline:\n- Images: Jimeng (即梦) ✓\n- Voiceover: Need a TTS API - could use MiniMax TTS (which is already in the pipeline), or OpenAI TTS, or Alibaba TTS\n\n\n- Video generation: Jimeng also supports video generation, so that could handle the animation piece\n\nLooking at the existing setup, the video-pipeline already has TTS capabilities through MiniMax. For the full workflow of generating scenes, creating voiceover, and composing the video, I need Jimeng for both image and video generation, the TTS service for narration, and potentially some video editing or composition tool to tie everything together.\n\nLet me check what the t2i/i2i skill actually supports and what video generation APIs are available.","thinkingSignature":"f6121f718dca54d66dae0244f5f52da31025076e87a7c02592cdd0d12aa4b08d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7218xxa7qeje_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/tts_request.json 2>/dev/null | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7218xxa7qeje_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"video generation\" 2>/dev/null | head -20; clawhub search \"tts\" 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":356,"cacheRead":27594,"cacheWrite":1484,"totalTokens":29524,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.0004272,"cacheRead":0.0008278199999999999,"cacheWrit