{"type":"message","id":"82ee5c34","parentId":"0046cd62","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:08:40.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the environment variables. There's a MINIMAX_API_KEY set. The minimax_response.json shows an \"invalid api key\" error for some MiniMax API call. But the TTS seems to be working based on the tts_request.json and tts_response.json.\n\nLet me summarize what's needed:\n\n1. **已有：** MiniMax API Key (TTS 可用，但调用时返回了 invalid api key，可能是接口问题)\n2. **需要：** Jimeng API Key (即梦文生图+图生视频)\n3. **需要确认：** MiniMax 视频生成是否可用（看 minimax_response.json 是 2049 invalid api key，可能是另一个接口）\n\n\n4. **建议方案：** 即梦负责图像和视频生成，因为它在这两个领域都有强大能力，而 MiniMax 的 TTS 技术已经足够用于旁白配音\n\n我应该给用户一个清晰的总结。","thinkingSignature":"c47f76fd50ca6cc8299c277a58e8acbaa06b1aed259f49c43f1edb510ed8c0d1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a5vc93wbjity_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/tts_response.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12571,"output":251,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31240,"cost":{"input":0.0037713,"output":0.0003012,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0046250399999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774350511476}}
