{"type":"message","id":"2275103b","parentId":"603cea93","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:27:36.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me prepare the TTS request. The narration needs to be concatenated into a single script. Let me use MiniMax TTS API. I noticed the MiniMax API key from the env is: `MINIMAX_API_KEY=sk-cp-dEJDwSZI46V_ys9hSxmyH3MT3kjnYJAkMGQK6fz38Imta8l5FmHU9stkSc8lqrT_xpeglsSQypkntDpu0xuJAYVxmkx_cpo3wEHseh_5pCi_HX_qX9X66-Y`\nThe earlier TTS request used `speech-01-turbo` model with `male-qn-qingse` voice. \n\nNow I'm constructing the full narration text for TTS conversion, combining all the segments into a single prompt for the MiniMax API.","thinkingSignature":"c9c8030b1d93872e64e13fcee8dd78123c974b7caf2633f79f16d8192007b6f5"},{"type":"text","text":"旁白文案写好了。现在生成配音：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hp0xgfmitnu9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && cat > tts_request_full.json << 'TSEOF'\n{\n  \"model\": \"speech-01-turbo\",\n  \"text\": \"公元前140年，汉武帝建元年间。匈奴南侵，边关告急。没有人知道，一个被遗弃的少年，将改变历史。他是郑青，父亲是雁门郡一个小吏。匈奴来时，父亲丢下他和母亲，独自逃命。母亲病死后，他被卖到了长安。八年后，他成了平阳侯府最下等的奴隶。没有名字，主人叫他小青。没人知道他是郑季的亲生儿子，也没人在乎。深夜，姐姐偷偷来看他。你疯了？！你是奴隶！正因为我是奴隶，参军，是我唯一的路。征兵处，他按下手印。官吏冷笑，又一个亡命徒。他转身，头也不回。月光下，姐姐追出来，泪流满面。这是我唯一的信物。你若死了，我烧给你。姐，我不会死。我还有账没算完。没有人知道，其中一个奴隶，将成为改变历史的那个人。天将降大任于斯人，必先苦其心志。\",\n  \"voice_setting\": {\n    \"voice_id\": \"male-qn-qingse\",\n    \"speed\": 0.9,\n    \"vol\": 1.0,\n    \"pitch\": 0\n  },\n  \"audio_setting\": {\n    \"sample_rate\": 32000,\n    \"bitrate\": 128000,\n    \"format\": \"mp3\",\n    \"channel\": 1\n  }\n}\nTSEOF\necho \"TTS request written\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18465,"output":554,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37437,"cost":{"input":0.0055395,"output":0.0006648,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00675684}},"stopReason":"toolUse",