{"type":"message","id":"b63d25a2","parentId":"3caaacd3","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:28:35.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`edge-tts` is available! That's a great free alternative. Let me use edge-tts to generate the voiceover. Edge TTS supports Chinese voices. Let me check what Chinese voices are available.\n\nThe voice.mp3 and voice-v2.mp3 files already exist and are valid MP3s - they were likely generated before. Let me check their duration and if they're suitable.","thinkingSignature":"b59d17adae5d847dcdc26d3eded6c46ed4ca0545cceaf1370166fe0a27f07f7c"},{"type":"text","text":"edge-tts 可用！用它来生成配音，同时开始写 Remotion 视频代码。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yh13vskttsai_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"edge-tts --list-voices | grep -i \"zh-CN\" | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yh13vskttsai_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && ffprobe -v quiet -show_entries format=duration -of csv=p=0 voice-v2.mp3 2>/dev/null || python3 -c \"\nimport subprocess\nr = subprocess.run(['ffprobe','-v','quiet','-show_entries','format=duration','-of','csv=p=0','voice-v2.mp3'], capture_output=True, text=True)\nprint('duration:', r.stdout.strip())\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22482,"output":264,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41164,"cost":{"input":0.0067446,"output":0.0003168,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00761394}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774351708700}}
