{"type":"message","id":"c9e3112f","parentId":"3a8b8398","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:28:46.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`voice-v2.mp3` is already about 51 seconds long, which is close to what we need for a 3-5 minute video (but this seems too short). Actually wait - the existing voice-v2.mp3 was for the phone charger script which was ~52 seconds. I need to generate a new voiceover for the Wei Qing script.\n\nLet me use edge-tts to generate the new narration. I'll use `zh-CN-YunxiNeural` or `zh-CN-YunjianNeural` for a male voice that fits the historical drama tone.\n\nNow let me:\n1. Generate TTS with edge-tts (male voice, slower speed for gravitas)\n\n\n2. Build the Remotion video\n3. Render\n\nFor Remotion, I need to plan the structure carefully - defining scenes with backgrounds and text overlays, then timing the voiceover to sync with the narrative beats. I'll write the narration to a file and generate the TTS while simultaneously working on the Remotion video code.","thinkingSignature":"e6dba0333db6d02124510d8399243b2b777e23285dcff9ffe0afc84b4232f49f"},{"type":"text","text":"好，用 edge-tts 生成配音男声，速度放慢增加历史感。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x1q5f4534did_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && cat > narration_full.txt << 'EOF'\n公元前140年，汉武帝建元年间。\n匈奴南侵，边关告急。\n没有人知道，一个被遗弃的少年，将改变历史。\n\n他是郑青，父亲是雁门郡一个小吏。\n匈奴来时，父亲丢下他和母亲，独自逃命。\n母亲病死后，他被卖到了长安。\n\n八年后，他成了平阳侯府最下等的奴隶。\n没有名字，主人叫他小青。\n没人知道他是郑季的亲生儿子，也没人在乎。\n\n深夜，姐姐偷偷来看他。\n你疯了？！你是奴隶！\n正因为我是奴隶，参军，是我唯一的路。\n\n征兵处，他按下手印。\n官吏冷笑，又一个亡命徒。\n他转身，头也不回。\n\n月光下，姐姐追出来，泪流满面。\n这是我唯一的信物。你若死了，我烧给你。\n姐，我不会死。我还有账没算完。\n\n没有人知道，其中一个奴隶，将成为改变历史的那个人。\n\n天将降大任于斯人，必先苦其心志。\nEOF\necho \"Narration written, lines: $(wc -l < narration_full.txt)\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23081,"output":487,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41986,"cost":{"input":0.006924299999