{"type":"message","id":"c32714d1","parentId":"8451bf35","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:28:53.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me generate the TTS using edge-tts. I'll use `zh-CN-YunjianNeural` (male, passionate) or `zh-CN-YunxiNeural` (male, lively/sunshine). For historical drama, `zh-CN-YunxiNeural` might work better.\n\nActually, let me check the voice again. The existing voice-v2.mp3 used `male-qn-qingse` which was a MiniMax voice. For edge-tts, I'll use `zh-CN-YunxiNeural` or `zh-CN-YunyangNeural` (professional for narration).\n\nLet me generate with edge-tts at a slower rate to give it gravitas.","thinkingSignature":"72743b9cd23affb202de5bada958cfb8217db5209b7b3d5281bd64b1d3c18e8c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jc7hue78ppvo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && edge-tts \\\n  --voice \"zh-CN-YunxiNeural\" \\\n  --rate \"-10%\" \\\n  --text \"$(cat narration_full.txt | tr '\\n' ' ')\" \\\n  --output narration_voice.mp3 \\\n  && ls -lh narration_voice.mp3 \\\n  && ffprobe -v quiet -show_entries format=duration -of csv=p=0 narration_voice.mp3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23684,"output":266,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42368,"cost":{"input":0.0071052,"output":0.0003192,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00797694}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774351726741}}
