{"type":"message","id":"76a49094","parentId":"40949fd4","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:29:02.646Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nzy42vag83xj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nusage: edge-tts [-h] [-t TEXT] [-f FILE] [-v VOICE] [-l] [--rate RATE]\n                [--volume VOLUME] [--pitch PITCH] [--write-media WRITE_MEDIA]\n                [--write-subtitles WRITE_SUBTITLES] [--proxy PROXY]\n                [--version]\n\nText-to-speech using Microsoft Edge's online TTS service.\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  -t TEXT, --text TEXT  what TTS will say\n  -f FILE, --file FILE  same as --text but read from file\n  -v VOICE, --voice VOICE\n                        voice for TTS. Default: en-US-EmmaMultilingualNeural\n  -l, --list-voices     lists available voices and exits\n  --rate RATE           set TTS rate. Default +0%.\n  --volume VOLUME       set TTS volume. Default +0%.\n  --pitch PITCH         set TTS pitch. Default +0Hz.\n  --write-media WRITE_MEDIA\n                        send media output to file instead of stdout\n  --write-subtitles WRITE_SUBTITLES\n                        send subtitle output to provided file instead of\n                        stderr\n  --proxy PROXY         use a proxy for TTS and voice list.\n  --version             show program's version number and exit"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":382,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nusage: edge-tts [-h] [-t TEXT] [-f FILE] [-v VOICE] [-l] [--rate RATE]\n                [--volume VOLUME] [--pitch PITCH] [--write-media WRITE_MEDIA]\n                [--write-subtitles WRITE_SUBTITLES] [--proxy PROXY]\n                [--version]\n\nText-to-speech using Microsoft Edge's online TTS service.\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  -t TEXT, --text TEXT  what TTS will say\n  -f FILE, --file FILE  same as --text but read from file\n  -v VOICE, --voice VOICE\n                        voice for TTS. Default: en-US-EmmaMultilingualNeural\n  -l, --list-voices     lists available voices and exits\n  --rate RATE           set TTS rate. Default +0%.\n  --volume VOLUME       set TTS volume. Default +0%.\n  --pitch PITCH         set TTS pitch. Default +0Hz.\n  --write-media WRITE_MEDIA\n                        send media output to file instead of stdout\n  --write-subtitles WRITE_SUBTITLES\n                        send subtitle output to provided file instead of\n                        stderr\n  --proxy PROXY         use a proxy for TTS and voice list.\n  --version             show program's version number and exit","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774351742642}}
{"type":"message","id":"74b9a47c","parentId":"76a49094","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:29:09.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `--rate` takes a value directly (not separated by space). Let me try:\n`edge-tts --rate +0%` - wait, the error says \"expected one argument\". This means when I use `--rate \"-10%\"` it should work... but the error is still about `--rate`. \n\nHmm, maybe it's because `--rate -10%` starts with `-` which is interpreted as a different argument. Let me try `--rate=-10%`.","thinkingSignature":"3dd08ddaa2475cca331280c697a14606539e6e46ca1f9424cfede5504453853b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rqxo1uggnm8w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && edge-tts \\\n  --voice \"zh-CN-YunxiNeural\" \\\n  --rate=+0% \\\n  --file \"narration_full.txt\" \\\n  --write-media \"narration_voice.mp3\" \\\n  --write-subtitles \"narration_voice.srt\" \\\n  && ls -lh narration_voice.mp3 narration_voice.srt \\\n  && echo \"Duration: $(ffprobe -v quiet -show_entries format=duration -of csv=p=0 narration_voice.mp3) sec\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24963,"output":248,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43629,"cost":{"input":0.0074889,"output":0.00029759999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00833904}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774351742647}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc9b2f9e","parentId":"74b9a47c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:29:16.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqxo1uggnm8w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n-rw-r--r-- 1 hochoy hochoy 417K Mar 24 19:29 narration_voice.mp3\n-rw-r--r-- 1 hochoy hochoy 1.7K Mar 24 19:29 narration_voice.srt\nDuration: 71.064000 sec"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6415,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n-rw-r--r-- 1 hochoy hochoy 417K Mar 24 19:29 narration_voice.mp3\n-rw-r--r-- 1 hochoy hochoy 1.7K Mar 24 19:29 narration_voice.srt\nDuration: 71.064000 sec","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774351756164}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b4a6250","parentId":"bc9b2f9e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:29:22.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The narration voice is 71 seconds long. That's good for a ~3-4 minute video with scene transitions and visual effects.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Parse the SRT to get timestamps for each segment\n2. Write the Remotion video code with proper timing\n3. Render the video\n\nLet me first check the SRT file to understand the timing.","thinkingSignature":"fcf3b1f3daa3ee9f78883aab7d17a32a68903b7e8f61917447ff54ddd08e56cb"},{"type":"text","text":"配音生成成功，71秒。开始写 Remotion 视频代码：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p3m4pjpbs3l1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/narration_voice.srt"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25385,"output":140,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43943,"cost":{"input":0.0076155,"output":0.000168,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00833604}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774351756171}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b34fb8f","parentId":"4b4a6250","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:29:22.239Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p3m4pjpbs3l1_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n1\n00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,950\n公元前140年，汉武帝建元年间。\n\n2\n00:00:03,900 --> 00:00:06,800\n匈奴南侵，边关告急。\n\n3\n00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:11,387\n没有人知道，一个被遗弃的少年，将改变历史。\n\n4\n00:00:11,387 --> 00:00:14,725\n他是郑青，父亲是雁门郡一个小吏。\n\n5\n00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:19,075\n匈奴来时，父亲丢下他和母亲，独自逃命。\n\n6\n00:00:19,075 --> 00:00:22,075\n母亲病死后，他被卖到了长安。\n\n7\n00:00:22,075 --> 00:00:26,050\n八年后，他成了平阳侯府最下等的奴隶。\n\n8\n00:00:26,050 --> 00:00:28,900\n没有名字，主人叫他小青。\n\n9\n00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:33,137\n没人知道他是郑季的亲生儿子，也没人在乎。\n\n10\n00:00:33,137 --> 00:00:35,912\n深夜，姐姐偷偷来看他。\n\n11\n00:00:35,912 --> 00:00:37,175\n你疯了？\n\n12\n00:00:37,175 --> 00:00:38,625\n你是奴隶！\n\n13\n00:00:38,625 --> 00:00:42,275\n正因为我是奴隶，参军，是我唯一的路。\n\n14\n00:00:42,275 --> 00:00:45,000\n征兵处，他按下手印。\n\n15\n00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,800\n官吏冷笑，又一个亡命徒。\n\n16\n00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:50,237\n他转身，头也不回。\n\n17\n00:00:50,237 --> 00:00:53,737\n月光下，姐姐追出来，泪流满面。\n\n18\n00:00:53,737 --> 00:00:55,475\n这是我唯一的信物。\n\n19\n00:00:55,475 --> 00:00:57,775\n你若死了，我烧给你。\n\n20\n00:00:57,775 --> 00:00:59,850\n姐，我不会死。\n\n21\n00:00:59,850 --> 00:01:01,612\n我还有账没算完。\n\n22\n00:01:01,612 --> 00:01:06,687\n没有人知道，其中一个奴隶，将成为改变历史的那个人。\n\n23\n00:01:06,687 --> 00:01:11,012\n天将降大任于斯人，必先苦其心志。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":24,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n1\n00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,950\n公元前140年，汉武帝建元年间。\n\n2\n00:00:03,900 --> 00:00:06,800\n匈奴南侵，边关告急。\n\n3\n00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:11,387\n没有人知道，一个被遗弃的少年，将改变历史。\n\n4\n00:00:11,387 --> 00:00:14,725\n他是郑青，父亲是雁门郡一个小吏。\n\n5\n00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:19,075\n匈奴来时，父亲丢下他和母亲，独自逃命。\n\n6\n00:00:19,075 --> 00:00:22,075\n母亲病死后，他被卖到了长安。\n\n7\n00:00:22,075 --> 00:00:26,050\n八年后，他成了平阳侯府最下等的奴隶。\n\n8\n00:00:26,050 --> 00:00:28,900\n没有名字，主人叫他小青。\n\n9\n00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:33,137\n没人知道他是郑季的亲生儿子，也没人在乎。\n\n10\n00:00:33,137 --> 00:00:35,912\n深夜，姐姐偷偷来看他。\n\n11\n00:00:35,912 --> 00:00:37,175\n你疯了？\n\n12\n00:00:37,175 --> 00:00:38,625\n你是奴隶！\n\n13\n00:00:38,625 --> 00:00:42,275\n正因为我是奴隶，参军，是我唯一的路。\n\n14\n00:00:42,275 --> 00:00:45,000\n征兵处，他按下手印。\n\n15\n00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,800\n官吏冷笑，又一个亡命徒。\n\n16\n00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:50,237\n他转身，头也不回。\n\n17\n00:00:50,237 --> 00:00:53,737\n月光下，姐姐追出来，泪流满面。\n\n18\n00:00:53,737 --> 00:00:55,475\n这是我唯一的信物。\n\n19\n00:00:55,475 --> 00:00:57,775\n你若死了，我烧给你。\n\n20\n00:00:57,775 --> 00:00:59,850\n姐，我不会死。\n\n21\n00:00:59,850 --> 00:01:01,612\n我还有账没算完。\n\n22\n00:01:01,612 --> 00:01:06,687\n没有人知道，其中一个奴隶，将成为改变历史的那个人。\n\n23\n00:01:06,687 --> 00:01:11,012\n天将降大任于斯人，必先苦其心志。","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774351762236}}
{"type":"message","id":"5811aee0","parentId":"8b34fb8f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:30:07.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the SRT with all the timestamps. I need to write the Remotion video code. The video is 71 seconds, at 30fps = 2130 frames.\n\nI need to:\n1. Define scenes with different background colors\n2. Show subtitles at the right times\n3. Have title cards for each major section\n4. Import the audio\n\nLet me write the Remotion code now.\n\nThe scenes based on the script:\n- 0-11s: Opening (dark/black)\n- 11-22s: 雪地弃子 (white/cold)\n- 22-33s: 侯府为奴 (dark/yellow)\n\n\n- 33-42s: 姐姐探望 (blue/moonlight)\n- 42-50s: 参军 (red/cold)\n- 50-59s: 告别 (blue/moonlight)\n- 59-66s: 踏上征途 (golden/morning)\n- 66-71s: 结尾黑幕 (black)\n\nI'll need to convert the SRT timestamps to frame numbers at 30fps to sync everything properly. Looking at the subtitle segments, I can map them to their corresponding scenes to ensure the timing aligns with the narrative arc.\n\nThe structure breaks down into eight distinct scenes, each with its own color palette and mood—from the cold white opening through the dark yellow tones of the palace slavery section, into the blue moonlight of the farewell, and finally the golden sunrise as he departs on his journey.\n\nNow I'm writing the Remotion code...","thinkingSignature":"39728dca5d3aafc0c0b579561936023c46c22ff216298f19943064f4b714d7f5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7v2ps6y6e9jw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline && cat > src/NarrationVideo.tsx << 'TSXEOF'\nimport {useVideoConfig, useCurrentFrame, interpolate, spring} from 'remotion';\nimport React from 'react';\n\n// Scene definitions: [startSec, endSec, bgColor, title, accentColor]\nconst SCENES: Array<[number, number, string, string, string]> = [\n  [0, 3, '#0a0a0f', '第1集 · 囚龙出渊', '#c9a84c'],\n  [3, 11, '#1a2a3a', '第一幕 · 雪地弃子', '#a8c4d4'],\n  [11, 22, '#2a2015', '第二幕 · 侯府为奴', '#8b7355'],\n  [22, 33, '#1a2535', '第三幕 · 深夜探望', '#7a9bb8'],\n  [33, 42, '#2a1520', '第四幕 · 血印参军', '#a85050'],\n  [42, 50, '#1a2535', '第五幕 · 月下离别', '#7a9bb8'],\n  [50, 59, '#3a2a10', '第六幕 · 踏上征途', '#c9a84c'],\n  [59, 71, '#0a0a0f', '', '#c9a84c'],\n];\n\n// Subtitle segments from SRT (startSec, endSec, text)\nconst SUBTITLES: Array<[number, number, string]> = [\n  [0, 3.95, '公元前140年，汉武帝建元年间。'],\n  [3.9, 6.8, '匈奴南侵，边关告急。'],\n  [6.8, 11.387, '没有人知道，一个被遗弃的少年，将改变历史。'],\n  [11.387, 14.725, '他是郑青，父亲是雁门郡一个小吏。'],\n  [14.725, 19.075, '匈奴来时，父亲丢下他和母亲，独自逃命。'],\n  [19.075, 22.075, '母亲病死后，他被卖到了长安。'],\n  [22.075, 26.05, '八年后，他成了平阳侯府最下等的奴隶。'],\n  [26.05, 28.9, '没有名字，主人叫他小青。'],\n  [28.9, 33.137, '没人知道他是郑季的亲生儿子，也没人在乎。'],\n  [33.137, 35.912, '深夜，姐姐偷偷来看他。'],\n  [35.912, 37.175, '你疯了？！'],\n  [37.175, 38.625, '你是奴隶！'],\n  [38.625, 42.275, '正因为我是奴隶，参军，是我唯一的路。'],\n  [42.275, 45.0, '征兵处，他按下手印。'],\n  [45.0, 47.8, '官吏冷笑，又一个亡命徒。'],\n  [47.8, 50.237, '他转身，头也不回。'],\n  [50.237, 53.737, '月光下，姐姐追出来，泪流满面。'],\n  [53.737, 55.475, '这是我唯一的信物。'],\n  [55.475, 57.775, '你若死了，我烧给你。'],\n  [57.775, 59.85, '姐，我不会死。'],\n  [59.85, 61.612, '我还有账没算完。'],\n  [61.612, 66.687, '没有人知道，其中一个奴隶，将成为改变历史的那个人。'],\n  [66.687, 71.0, '天将降大任于斯人，必先苦其心志。'],\n];\n\nfunction getSceneAt(frame: number, fps: number) {\n  const sec = frame / fps;\n  for (const [start, end, bg, title, accent] of SCENES) {\n    if (sec >= start && sec < end) return {bg, title, accent, sceneStart: start};\n  }\n  return null;\n}\n\nfunction SubtitleLine({start, end, text, frame, fps}: {\n  start: number; end: number; text: string; frame: number; fps: number;\n}) {\n  const sec = frame / fps;\n  if (sec < start || sec > end) return null;\n  const progress = Math.min(1, (sec - start) / 0.3);\n  const fadeOut = sec > end - 0.5 ? (end - sec) / 0.5 : 1;\n  const opacity = progress * fadeOut;\n  const translateY = interpolate(opacity, [0, 1], [20, 0]);\n  return (\n    <div style={{\n      position: 'absolute',\n      bottom: 120,\n      left: 0,\n      right: 0,\n      textAlign: 'center',\n      opacity,\n      transform: `translateY(${translateY}px)`,\n    }}>\n      <div style={{\n        display: 'inline-block',\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.75)',\n        padding: '16px 40px',\n        borderRadius: 4,\n        border: '1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)',\n        fontSize: 32,\n        fontFamily: 'Noto Sans CJK SC, sans-serif',\n        color: '#f0e6d3',\n        maxWidth: 900,\n        lineHeight: 1.6,\n        textShadow: '0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.8)',\n      }}>\n        {text}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nfunction SceneTitle({title, accent, frame, fps, sceneStart}: {\n  title: string; accent: string; frame: number; fps: number; sceneStart: number;\n}) {\n  const sec = frame / fps;\n  const progress = (sec - sceneStart) / 1.5;\n  if (progress <= 0 || progress > 3) return null;\n  const opacity = progress < 1 ? progress : interpolate(progress, [1, 2], [1, 0]);\n  return (\n    <div style={{\n      position: 'absolute',\n      top: 80,\n      left: 0,\n      right: 0,\n      textAlign: 'center',\n      opacity,\n    }}>\n      <div style={{\n        fontSize: 22,\n        fontFamily: 'Noto Sans CJK SC, sans-serif',\n        color: accent,\n        letterSpacing: 6,\n        textTransform: 'uppercase',\n        textShadow: `0 0 20px ${accent}`,\n      }}>\n        {title}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nfunction DecorativeLine({accent, frame, fps, sceneStart}: {\n  accent: string; frame: number; fps: number; sceneStart: number;\n}) {\n  const sec = frame / fps;\n  const progress = (sec - sceneStart) / 0.8;\n  if (progress <= 0 || progress > 2) return null;\n  const width = interpolate(Math.min(progress, 1), [0, 1], [0, 200]);\n  const opacity = progress > 1.5 ? interpolate(progress, [1.5, 2], [1, 0]) : 1;\n  return (\n    <div style={{\n      position: 'absolute',\n      top: 120,\n      left: '50%',\n      transform: `translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%)`,\n      width,\n      height: 2,\n      background: accent,\n      opacity,\n      boxShadow: `0 0 10px ${accent}`,\n    }} />\n  );\n}\n\nexport const NarrationVideo: React.FC = () => {\n  const {fps, width, height} = useVideoConfig();\n  const frame = useCurrentFrame();\n  const scene = getSceneAt(frame, fps);\n\n  if (!scene) return null;\n  const {bg, title, accent, sceneStart} = scene;\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{\n      flex: 1,\n      backgroundColor: bg,\n      justifyContent: 'center',\n      alignItems: 'center',\n      display: 'flex',\n      position: 'relative',\n      overflow: 'hidden',\n    }}>\n      {/* Background gradient */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute',\n        inset: 0,\n        background: `radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, ${bg}44 0%, ${bg} 70%)`,\n      }} />\n\n      {/* Decorative corner lines */}\n      <div style={{position: 'absolute', top: 30, left: 40, width: 60, height: 1, background: `${accent}66`}} />\n      <div style={{position: 'absolute', top: 30, left: 40, width: 1, height: 40, background: `${accent}66`}} />\n      <div style={{position: 'absolute', bottom: 30, right: 40, width: 60, height: 1, background: `${accent}66`}} />\n      <div style={{position: 'absolute', bottom: 30, right: 40, width: 1, height: 40, background: `${accent}66`}} />\n\n      {/* Scene title */}\n      {title && (\n        <SceneTitle\n          title={title}\n          accent={accent}\n          frame={frame}\n          fps={fps}\n          sceneStart={sceneStart}\n        />\n      )}\n\n      {/* Subtitle */}\n      {SUBTITLES.map(([start, end, text], i) => (\n        <SubtitleLine\n          key={i}\n          start={start}\n          end={end}\n          text={text}\n          frame={frame}\n          fps={fps}\n        />\n      ))}\n\n      {/* Bottom timeline dots */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute',\n        bottom: 40,\n        left: '50%',\n        transform: 'translateX(-50%)',\n        display: 'flex',\n        gap: 8,\n      }}>\n        {SCENES.map(([start, end], i) => {\n          const isActive = frame / fps >= start && frame / fps < end;\n          return (\n            <div key={i} style={{\n              width: isActive ? 24 : 6,\n              height: 6,\n              borderRadius: 3,\n              background: isActive ? accent : `${accent}44`,\n              transition: 'all 0.3s',\n            }} />\n          );\n        })}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n};\nTSXEOF\necho \"Written NarrationVideo.tsx\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":26266,"output":2697,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47381,"cost":{"input":0.0078798,"output":0.0032364,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01166874}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774351762240}}
