{"type":"message","id":"9ab9de7d","parentId":"b4ab4457","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:57:44.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can see there's `qwen-image` skill on ClawHub which could do image generation. Let me think about what the user is asking:\n\n\"qwen3.5 plus text+image\" - they're asking if Qwen3.5 with text+image capabilities can make short drama or comic videos.\n\nThe answer is:\n1. Qwen3.5 is a language model with vision (can understand images)\n2. For VIDEO generation, it would need:\n   - An image generation model (like 通义万相/Qwen Image)\n   - An image-to-video model (like Wan/I2V)\n   - Qwen could orchestrate/generate prompts for these\n3. There's already a `qwen-image` skill on ClawHub\n\nSo the user seems to have Qwen access and is asking if this pipeline could work for short drama/comic videos. The short answer is yes, Qwen could generate the prompts and orchestrate the image and video generation. Let me give them a clear assessment.","thinkingSignature":"edda15bd224ae71658b37ce26d6c8cfc5596b080454245692ab6362955ca8c50"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n**可以，但需要组合工具。** Qwen3.5 本身是语言模型，生成视频需要配合专门的图像/视频生成模型。\n\n**Qwen 在这个 pipeline 里能做的：**\n- 生成剧本/分镜描述\n- 生成 AI 生图的 prompt（提示词）\n- 编排整个制作流程\n\n**但 Qwen 不能直接生成视频**，需要配合：\n- **通义万相**（Qwen Image）— 生成汉朝场景图\n- **视频生成模型**（即梦/Wan等）— 图生视频\n\n---\n\n**你现在已有的能力对比：**\n\n| 能力 | Qwen3.5 | 通义万相 | 即梦 |\n|------|---------|---------|------|\n| 生成生图 prompt | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| 文生图 | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| 图生视频 | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 编排流程 | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n\n**最理想的漫剧制作流程：**\n```\nQwen3.5（生成prompt） → 通义万相（生图） → 即梦（图生视频） → Remotion（合成配音字幕）\n```\n\n你有通义万相（qwen-image）的 API Key 吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57824,"output":479,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76721,"cost":{"input":0.0173472,"output":0.0005748,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01847454}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774353451572}}
{"type":"message","id":"445ec3e6","parentId":"9ab9de7d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:05:44.638Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5313afbbe0b4b297cd62a6fa367\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 20:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5313afbbe0b4b297cd62a6fa367]\nou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352: 可以使用minimax的生图模型来生成图片吗"}],"timestamp":1774353944633}}
{"type":"message","id":"abacbbb6","parentId":"445ec3e6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:05:59.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can use MiniMax's image generation model. Let me check the MiniMax API documentation. The MiniMax API key is available in the environment, and I know MiniMax has some image capabilities. Let me try to check if there's a MiniMax image generation API.","thinkingSignature":"24e386e5d2edca7ed34718836497df1a1b3693f44760b654e6132a931971f8cd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ru7qd6xgrk3d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/oauth2/token\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"grant_type\":\"client_credentials\",\"client_id\":\"'\"$MINIMAX_API_KEY\"'\"}' 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('access_token','')[:30])\" 2>/dev/null)\necho \"Token: $TOKEN\"\n\n# Try MiniMax image generation API\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/image_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"image-01\",\"prompt\":\"Ancient Chinese Han dynasty soldier, cold battlefield, snow, dramatic lighting\",\"image_size\":\"16:9\"}' \\\n  | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(json.dumps(d, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\" 2>/dev/null | head -20","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":330,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":76491,"totalTokens":76911,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.009178919999999998,"total":0.009601919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774353944636}}
