{"type":"message","id":"a5a64d12","parentId":"ab6a5fd2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:27:26.422Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me spawn a subagent to handle the image generation in parallel while I continue with other work.","thinkingSignature":"2ed8f65da8a8b40215a7f81c9ccab77c6b162f392d1bd003efcfd00ff399867e"},{"type":"text","text":"6 个场景我会用子进程并行生成。先生成 prompt，同时推送到后台：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jy2pzzssacbu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/gen_scenes.sh << 'SCRIPT'\n#!/bin/bash\ncd /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/scenes\nAPI_KEY=$1\n\ndeclare -A PROMPTS=(\n  [\"scene1\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, vast snow plain battlefield, smoke and fire, Mongolian Xiongnu raiders on horseback attacking, a thin weak boy aged 6-8 hiding under a broken cart peering through gaps with terrified determined eyes, heavy snow falling, cinematic dramatic lighting, cold blue white tones, epic historical war scene, photorealistic film still\"\n  [\"scene2\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, inside a dirty horse stable at a nobleman mansion, a thin teenage boy slave with old scars on his face being kicked by a fat cruel steward, other slaves working in background, dim earthy yellow lighting, oppressed atmosphere, dramatic cinematic composition, photorealistic film still\"\n  [\"scene3\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, back garden of a princess mansion at dusk, a beautiful young woman dancer in elegant Hanfu dancing gracefully while a thin teenage boy watches from behind a rockery, warm golden sunset light, melancholy atmosphere, cinematic, photorealistic film still\"\n  [\"scene4\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, bustling city gate of Chang AN, imperial messenger on horseback rushing through crowds screaming匈奴犯边, a determined teenage slave boy standing in the crowd looking at conscription notice on city wall, dramatic肃杀 red tones, cinematic documentary style, photorealistic film still\"\n  [\"scene5\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, moonlit night, back gate of a nobleman mansion, a young woman in Hanfu pressing a cloth to a teenage boy slave with tears on her face, boy carrying simple bundle, emotional farewell scene, silver blue moonlight, dramatic cinematic, photorealistic film still\"\n  [\"scene6\"]=\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, dawn官道 outside Chang AN city, long column of new recruits marching northward, a teenage boy walking at the end of the column looking back at the city, morning golden sunlight, epic scale, hopeful yet somber mood, cinematic wideshot, photorealistic film still\"\n)\n\nfor name in scene1 scene2 scene3 scene4 scene5 scene6; do\n  echo \"Generating $name...\"\n  RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/image_generation\" \\\n    -H \"Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"$(jq -n --arg prompt \"${PROMPTS[$name]}\" '{\n      model: \"image-01\",\n      prompt: $prompt,\n      image_size: \"16:9\"\n    }')\")\n  \n  URL=$(echo \"$RESP\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('data',{}).get('image_urls',[''])[0])\" 2>/dev/null)\n  if [ -n \"$URL\" ]; then\n    curl -s -o \"${name}.jpg\" \"$URL\"\n    echo \"$name done: $(ls -lh ${name}.jpg)\"\n  else\n    echo \"$name FAILED: $RESP\"\n  fi\ndone\necho \"All done!\"\nSCRIPT\nchmod +x /tmp/gen_scenes.sh\necho \"Script ready\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61878,"output":762,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81058,"cost":{"input":0.0185634,"output":0.0009144,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02003034}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774355222685}}
