{"type":"message","id":"f2ac4a9b","parentId":"2bfe5f9d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:30:10.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"5 out of 6 scenes generated successfully. Scene 2 failed with \"input new_sensitive\" which means the content was flagged as sensitive. Let me retry scene 2 with a less graphic prompt - instead of showing violence explicitly, I'll make it about the harsh conditions in the stable.","thinkingSignature":"5b185654db0f2553f1da5b48532b3b39768b77415207700fa91a6fba1d90aaab"},{"type":"text","text":"5/6 完成！Scene 2 触发了敏感词审核，重试一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t07ax1o7k2jr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/image_generation\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"image-01\",\"prompt\":\"Ancient China Han Dynasty, dark dirty horse stable of wealthy mansion at dawn, thin teenage boy with worn clothes and scars on face crouched in corner amidst hay and horse dung, other slaves working in background in cold wind, dim yellow brown lighting oppressive atmosphere, cinematic dramatic photorealistic film still\",\"image_size\":\"16:9\"}')\nURL=$(echo \"$RESP\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('data',{}).get('image_urls',[''])[0])\" 2>/dev/null)\necho \"Response: $RESP\"\nif [ -n \"$URL\" ]; then curl -s -o /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/scenes/scene2.jpg \"$URL\"; echo \"scene2 done: $(ls -lh /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/projects/video-pipeline/scenes/scene2.jpg)\"; else echo \"FAILED\"; fi","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65647,"output":376,"cacheRead":18418,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84441,"cost":{"input":0.0196941,"output":0.00045119999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0005525399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02069784}},"stopRe